1
00:01:24,120 --> 00:01:24,640
Wonderful!

2
00:01:25,280 --> 00:01:27,400
Bravo, bravo, bravo!

3
00:01:27,760 --> 00:01:28,280
Excellent!

4
00:01:28,599 --> 00:01:29,680
Simply brilliant!

5
00:01:30,120 --> 00:01:30,439
Wonderful!

6
00:01:30,560 --> 00:01:31,879
Young Masters, please enjoy yourselves.

7
00:01:32,480 --> 00:01:34,159
I shall take my leave now.

8
00:01:36,680 --> 00:01:37,319
Don't be in such a hurry.

9
00:01:37,560 --> 00:01:38,239
Wait, wait...

10
00:01:38,719 --> 00:01:39,319
Lady Nanzhi.

11
00:01:40,599 --> 00:01:41,200
Lady Nanzhi.

12
00:01:41,519 --> 00:01:43,079
This is a poem I wrote for you.

13
00:01:43,439 --> 00:01:45,439
I hope you won't find it lacking.

14
00:01:45,879 --> 00:01:46,560
Lady Nanzhi.

15
00:01:47,120 --> 00:01:49,879
A Night-Luminous Pearl from foreign lands.

16
00:01:50,879 --> 00:01:52,280
This one's nice.

17
00:01:52,920 --> 00:01:53,519
I'll take it.

18
00:01:54,480 --> 00:01:55,120
Lady Yudie.

19
00:01:55,599 --> 00:01:56,680
I spent a fortune

20
00:01:56,840 --> 00:01:57,680
to get this Dangling hairpin made for you.

21
00:01:58,040 --> 00:01:59,040
I hope you like it.

22
00:01:59,400 --> 00:02:00,680
This one's nice too.

23
00:02:01,000 --> 00:02:01,719
How thoughtful of you.

24
00:02:03,359 --> 00:02:04,560
Make way, make way, make way.

25
00:02:05,000 --> 00:02:05,560
Step aside.

26
00:02:08,039 --> 00:02:09,639
Isn't this the Eldest Young Master Ning?

27
00:02:11,080 --> 00:02:12,639
What's this guy doing here?

28
00:02:13,599 --> 00:02:14,560
Eldest Young Master Ning.

29
00:02:14,759 --> 00:02:15,360
Lady Nanzhi.

30
00:02:15,840 --> 00:02:17,039
I had someone specially

31
00:02:17,319 --> 00:02:18,560
seek out this Jade flute for you.

32
00:02:19,560 --> 00:02:20,639
I hope you like it.

33
00:02:24,719 --> 00:02:25,759
Thank you, Young Master Ning.

34
00:02:27,199 --> 00:02:27,960
You're welcome.

35
00:02:28,319 --> 00:02:29,280
As long as you like it.

36
00:02:30,680 --> 00:02:31,960
That's all that matters.

37
00:02:32,280 --> 00:02:34,439
Means I've got a chance tonight.

38
00:02:38,560 --> 00:02:39,039
Old Pan,

39
00:02:39,439 --> 00:02:41,280
just sit back and watch.

40
00:02:42,639 --> 00:02:43,319
I'm

41
00:02:44,599 --> 00:02:45,919
just an uncultured warrior.

42
00:02:46,439 --> 00:02:47,759
I'm not worthy of Lady Nanzhi.

43
00:02:48,280 --> 00:02:50,000
Just watching makes me

44
00:02:51,240 --> 00:02:51,759
happy.

45
00:02:52,639 --> 00:02:53,879
What are you chickening out for?

46
00:02:54,240 --> 00:02:55,919
We brothers have got your back.

47
00:02:56,080 --> 00:02:57,199
For literary talent, you've got me.

48
00:02:57,919 --> 00:02:58,639
For martial prowess,

49
00:02:59,240 --> 00:03:00,199
you've got us.

50
00:03:02,360 --> 00:03:03,000
No need.

51
00:03:03,879 --> 00:03:04,639
In the Imperial Uncle case,

52
00:03:05,280 --> 00:03:06,080
you saved my life.

53
00:03:06,680 --> 00:03:09,000
Today I'm returning the favor.

54
00:03:09,560 --> 00:03:10,080
Really, there's no need.

55
00:03:10,159 --> 00:03:11,039
No need, no need.

56
00:03:11,719 --> 00:03:12,159
Come on.

57
00:03:12,759 --> 00:03:13,400
Lady Nanzhi.

58
00:03:13,800 --> 00:03:15,360
This here is our leader,

59
00:03:15,520 --> 00:03:17,000
Pan Yucheng, the Golden Guard Pan.

60
00:03:17,199 --> 00:03:19,360
You could say he's dashing and elegant,

61
00:03:19,479 --> 00:03:20,479
a fine figure of a man.

62
00:03:20,599 --> 00:03:22,400
Strong as an ox, healthy appetite.

63
00:03:22,560 --> 00:03:24,280
Skilled in letters and arms, and upright.

64
00:03:24,479 --> 00:03:26,360
And he's long admired you.

65
00:03:29,919 --> 00:03:31,280
Lady Nanzhi, pay them no mind.

66
00:03:31,719 --> 00:03:32,680
I know these people.

67
00:03:33,159 --> 00:03:34,319
Crude and vulgar,

68
00:03:34,680 --> 00:03:35,840
with filthy minds.

69
00:03:35,960 --> 00:03:37,120
You, get out of the way.

70
00:03:37,919 --> 00:03:38,520
Lady Nanzhi,

71
00:03:38,879 --> 00:03:39,759
our Old Pan here

72
00:03:39,879 --> 00:03:41,280
has composed a poem for you.

73
00:03:46,439 --> 00:03:49,000
A Country bumpkin writing poetry?

74
00:03:49,319 --> 00:03:51,000
That's a first.

75
00:03:51,439 --> 00:03:54,840
He probably doesn't know Tonal patterns.

76
00:03:55,280 --> 00:03:56,319
Hold on.

77
00:03:58,240 --> 00:03:59,240
This Tonal patterns guy here,

78
00:03:59,719 --> 00:04:01,240
could you shut your mouth?

79
00:04:02,400 --> 00:04:04,159
If you can't listen to reason,

80
00:04:04,680 --> 00:04:06,599
I happen to know how to use my fists.

81
00:04:07,879 --> 00:04:08,599
What do you think you're doing?

82
00:04:08,719 --> 00:04:10,000
Do you know who I am?

83
00:04:11,199 --> 00:04:12,919
Then do you know who he is?

84
00:04:14,400 --> 00:04:15,719
A Country bumpkin,

85
00:04:16,240 --> 00:04:17,839
some unworthy nobody.

86
00:04:19,160 --> 00:04:20,879
This nobody you speak of

87
00:04:21,040 --> 00:04:22,519
is the man who killed the Imperial Uncle,

88
00:04:22,839 --> 00:04:24,040
Ning Chen.

89
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:33,000
Don't say such things again.

90
00:04:33,319 --> 00:04:34,480
If word reaches His Majesty,

91
00:04:35,560 --> 00:04:36,360
it'll bring trouble to Chen.

92
00:04:36,959 --> 00:04:37,680
Then we can mention

93
00:04:37,800 --> 00:04:39,079
Ning Chen's other identity.

94
00:04:40,480 --> 00:04:41,160
That's right.

95
00:04:42,560 --> 00:04:43,959
Let me tell you all something.

96
00:04:44,639 --> 00:04:45,680
The Great Scholar of the Hanlin Academy

97
00:04:45,839 --> 00:04:48,079
once told my brother Ning Chen

98
00:04:48,720 --> 00:04:51,519
that he's the Poet Immortal reborn.

99
00:04:53,759 --> 00:04:55,399
Poet Immortal reborn?

100
00:04:55,720 --> 00:04:56,720
What audacity!

101
00:04:57,079 --> 00:04:59,439
If you have the skill, write a poem now.

102
00:05:00,199 --> 00:05:00,839
Damn it.

103
00:05:01,279 --> 00:05:02,240
A chance to shine like this

104
00:05:02,399 --> 00:05:04,199
should be mine, Eldest Young Master Ning.

105
00:05:04,480 --> 00:05:06,439
Why should a bastard like you show off?

106
00:05:07,120 --> 00:05:07,600
Exactly.

107
00:05:08,319 --> 00:05:10,160
Li Hanru, Chancellor of the Academy,

108
00:05:10,240 --> 00:05:11,639
is famous for empty flattery.

109
00:05:12,120 --> 00:05:13,480
He casually praised you,

110
00:05:13,759 --> 00:05:15,240
and now you're getting smug about it?

111
00:05:17,639 --> 00:05:18,480
Showing off, are we?

112
00:05:18,959 --> 00:05:19,439
Oh, come on.

113
00:05:21,439 --> 00:05:21,879
I...

114
00:05:22,560 --> 00:05:23,079
Chen,

115
00:05:23,439 --> 00:05:25,360
let's compose one and show him.

116
00:05:26,040 --> 00:05:27,480
Alright then,

117
00:05:28,279 --> 00:05:28,800
here's one.

118
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:29,720
Go on.

119
00:05:38,360 --> 00:05:41,240
The warm southern branch blooms early,

120
00:05:41,720 --> 00:05:45,319
letting her reign as queen of all flowers.

121
00:05:45,800 --> 00:05:49,439
Unrivaled by time, holding spring within,

122
00:05:50,040 --> 00:05:51,680
moved by your longing...

123
00:05:52,439 --> 00:05:53,000
seeking...

124
00:05:53,800 --> 00:05:54,399
a smile.

125
00:05:57,279 --> 00:05:57,759
There.

126
00:05:59,879 --> 00:06:02,000
Bravo, bravo, bravo!

127
00:06:03,000 --> 00:06:04,000
Wonderful, wonderful!

128
00:06:04,160 --> 00:06:05,040
This poem,

129
00:06:05,319 --> 00:06:07,920
Not quite 'To leave purity in the world',

130
00:06:08,959 --> 00:06:11,360
is still a rare masterpiece.

131
00:06:11,680 --> 00:06:13,319
Especially the first line,

132
00:06:13,600 --> 00:06:16,319
which contains Lady Nanzhi's name!

133
00:06:17,319 --> 00:06:18,399
With this poem out,

134
00:06:18,720 --> 00:06:19,879
Lady Nanzhi's worth

135
00:06:20,120 --> 00:06:21,399
will multiply many times over.

136
00:06:21,519 --> 00:06:22,759
Indeed, indeed.

137
00:06:24,879 --> 00:06:27,120
Old Pan is upright and honest,

138
00:06:27,439 --> 00:06:28,319
steady and hardworking.

139
00:06:28,639 --> 00:06:31,279
Choosing him is definitely the right call.

140
00:06:32,079 --> 00:06:33,120
Now look at this one.

141
00:06:34,319 --> 00:06:35,879
Pale face,

142
00:06:36,279 --> 00:06:37,399
sunken eyes,

143
00:06:37,920 --> 00:06:39,279
the very picture of Excessive debauchery.

144
00:06:40,839 --> 00:06:41,519
Who knows,

145
00:06:41,720 --> 00:06:43,199
he might even carry some filthy disease.

146
00:06:45,560 --> 00:06:46,000
I...

147
00:06:47,120 --> 00:06:47,600
No, you...

148
00:06:47,720 --> 00:06:48,800
What "you"?

149
00:06:50,519 --> 00:06:51,560
Bringing some shabby flute,

150
00:06:51,800 --> 00:06:53,560
thinking you can win over Lady Nanzhi?

151
00:06:54,160 --> 00:06:56,160
What flute hasn't Lady Nanzhi seen?

152
00:06:56,639 --> 00:06:59,920
Would she ever fancy the likes of you?

153
00:07:02,920 --> 00:07:03,639
Ning Chen!

154
00:07:04,079 --> 00:07:04,600
What?

155
00:07:05,480 --> 00:07:06,920
Eldest Young Master Ning wants to play?

156
00:07:11,040 --> 00:07:12,040
You, you, you...

157
00:07:12,160 --> 00:07:14,000
You're standing up for him, are you?

158
00:07:16,759 --> 00:07:18,360
Ning Chen is our brother.

159
00:07:18,680 --> 00:07:19,720
What's wrong with standing up for him?

160
00:07:21,639 --> 00:07:22,759
What are you bulging your eyes at us for?

161
00:07:23,399 --> 00:07:25,279
Mind if we gouge those eyeballs out

162
00:07:25,319 --> 00:07:26,600
and stomp on them like firecrackers?

163
00:07:29,800 --> 00:07:30,240
Ning Chen,

164
00:07:34,000 --> 00:07:34,399
are you alright?

165
00:07:34,519 --> 00:07:35,319
The Eldest Young Master Ning is hurt!

166
00:07:35,439 --> 00:07:36,319
Look at my leg!

167
00:07:38,480 --> 00:07:39,600
Today's humiliation,

168
00:07:40,279 --> 00:07:40,920
I'll repay it someday.

169
00:07:41,040 --> 00:07:41,639
Quick, go report it!

170
00:07:42,519 --> 00:07:43,439
This poem,

171
00:07:43,959 --> 00:07:44,839
did he write it,

172
00:07:45,360 --> 00:07:46,360
or did you give it to him?

173
00:07:53,480 --> 00:07:54,399
Ning Chen wrote it.

174
00:07:57,759 --> 00:07:58,360
Just as I thought.

175
00:07:58,720 --> 00:07:59,360
After all this time,

176
00:07:59,800 --> 00:08:01,120
he hasn't improved one bit.

177
00:08:01,639 --> 00:08:02,439
Golden Guard Pan,

178
00:08:02,959 --> 00:08:04,199
if you don't mind,

179
00:08:04,839 --> 00:08:05,959
won't you come to my chamber

180
00:08:07,120 --> 00:08:09,600
for a cup of tea?

181
00:08:10,399 --> 00:08:11,439
Gladly.

182
00:08:12,519 --> 00:08:15,560
Lady Nanzhi has chosen a Favored guest!

183
00:08:16,639 --> 00:08:18,279
To enter one of The Twelve Houses

184
00:08:18,680 --> 00:08:20,360
is an immense honor indeed.

185
00:08:23,160 --> 00:08:23,639
Go on.

186
00:08:24,079 --> 00:08:24,519
Go!

187
00:08:24,879 --> 00:08:25,439
Go!

188
00:08:36,600 --> 00:08:37,879
A perfect shot!

189
00:08:38,000 --> 00:08:39,200
An unforgettable night!

190
00:08:39,440 --> 00:08:40,679
Unstoppable!

191
00:08:42,399 --> 00:08:43,200
Go for it!

192
00:08:44,720 --> 00:08:46,360
Lady Yudie, Lady Yudie!

193
00:08:46,679 --> 00:08:47,360
Lady Yudie!

194
00:08:48,080 --> 00:08:49,759
Brother, we're brothers, right?

195
00:08:50,240 --> 00:08:50,799
No, we're not.

196
00:08:51,279 --> 00:08:52,080
We are brothers.

197
00:08:52,480 --> 00:08:53,039
Listen,

198
00:08:53,159 --> 00:08:54,000
write me a poem too.

199
00:08:54,720 --> 00:08:55,559
I've liked Yudie

200
00:08:56,080 --> 00:08:56,799
for a long time.

201
00:08:56,840 --> 00:08:58,120
Come on, just help me out.

202
00:08:58,559 --> 00:08:59,159
Then I'll...

203
00:08:59,320 --> 00:08:59,840
You what?

204
00:09:00,159 --> 00:09:00,840
You're already married!

205
00:09:00,960 --> 00:09:01,799
I'm still single!

206
00:09:01,919 --> 00:09:03,120
What's wrong with asking Chen for a poem?

207
00:09:03,120 --> 00:09:03,639
Tell you what,

208
00:09:04,399 --> 00:09:05,000
if it works out,

209
00:09:05,360 --> 00:09:06,879
I'll call you my godfather.

210
00:09:07,320 --> 00:09:08,879
Godfather? This is my real dad!

211
00:09:09,240 --> 00:09:09,799
You what?

212
00:09:09,919 --> 00:09:10,600
You're about to be a father yourself,

213
00:09:10,720 --> 00:09:11,720
and you're still stirring up trouble?

214
00:09:11,879 --> 00:09:12,559
There's more than one girl here.

215
00:09:12,679 --> 00:09:13,440
Why are you fighting over her?

216
00:09:13,559 --> 00:09:14,559
Look at that greasy head of yours.

217
00:09:14,600 --> 00:09:15,240
Young Master Ning.

218
00:09:16,879 --> 00:09:19,039
I wonder if I might have the honor

219
00:09:19,320 --> 00:09:21,279
of inviting you to share a cup of wine.

220
00:09:22,159 --> 00:09:23,200
Are you talking to me?

221
00:09:23,480 --> 00:09:24,639
Not you.

222
00:09:26,799 --> 00:09:28,799
Of course.

223
00:09:29,879 --> 00:09:30,799
What do you mean, "of course"?

224
00:09:30,919 --> 00:09:31,279
Hold on.

225
00:09:31,360 --> 00:09:32,600
Why is she inviting him for a drink?

226
00:09:32,879 --> 00:09:34,200
All he can do is write a few cheesy poems.

227
00:09:34,320 --> 00:09:34,720
Besides,

228
00:09:34,879 --> 00:09:36,039
I'm better looking than he is.

229
00:09:36,200 --> 00:09:37,639
Why isn't she asking me for a drink?

230
00:09:38,000 --> 00:09:39,080
When did you go blind?

231
00:09:39,159 --> 00:09:40,120
Get lost, go play somewhere else.

232
00:09:40,919 --> 00:09:41,480
Ning.

233
00:09:42,879 --> 00:09:44,000
Lady Yudie has already asked.

234
00:09:44,200 --> 00:09:46,679
Why not compose a poem for her too?

235
00:09:47,240 --> 00:09:48,000
Compose, my ass!

236
00:09:48,200 --> 00:09:48,720
Really?

237
00:09:49,559 --> 00:09:51,960
Would Yudie have such an honor?

238
00:09:53,320 --> 00:09:53,799
Yes.

239
00:09:54,559 --> 00:09:55,200
Of course.

240
00:10:06,440 --> 00:10:07,240
Sanniang.

241
00:10:09,080 --> 00:10:09,559
I've got it.

242
00:10:10,679 --> 00:10:14,120
After countless calls, she finally appears,

243
00:10:14,879 --> 00:10:18,799
her face half-hidden behind her pipa.

244
00:10:20,080 --> 00:10:24,919
A few twists, a pluck of the strings,

245
00:10:25,759 --> 00:10:30,120
Emotion flows before the melody begins.

246
00:10:30,679 --> 00:10:31,919
Wonderful!

247
00:10:32,120 --> 00:10:33,639
A brilliant poem!

248
00:10:35,639 --> 00:10:36,840
Truly eye-opening!

249
00:10:37,039 --> 00:10:37,639
What a poem!

250
00:10:37,639 --> 00:10:38,120
Move aside.

251
00:10:39,639 --> 00:10:40,759
Is Lady Yudie pleased?

252
00:10:41,279 --> 00:10:42,279
Yudie is most pleased.

253
00:10:42,919 --> 00:10:44,399
To receive a poem from you, Young Master,

254
00:10:44,960 --> 00:10:46,360
I shall have no regrets in this life.

255
00:10:47,120 --> 00:10:47,759
Young Master,

256
00:10:48,080 --> 00:10:49,600
what is the title of this poem?

257
00:10:50,639 --> 00:10:51,360
"For Yudie."

258
00:10:54,320 --> 00:10:55,240
Thank you, Young Master.

259
00:10:56,919 --> 00:10:58,279
If you don't mind, Young Master,

260
00:10:59,200 --> 00:11:02,559
would you join me in my room for a drink?

261
00:11:05,240 --> 00:11:05,759
This...

262
00:11:05,799 --> 00:11:07,600
One poem and he's taking Lady Yudie away?

263
00:11:07,759 --> 00:11:08,399
That easy?

264
00:11:08,759 --> 00:11:09,200
This...

265
00:11:09,360 --> 00:11:10,480
I should have done the same!

266
00:11:10,600 --> 00:11:11,279
Exactly.

267
00:11:14,120 --> 00:11:14,879
Lady Yudie,

268
00:11:15,440 --> 00:11:16,799
go easy on our Ning.

269
00:11:17,000 --> 00:11:19,320
He's never been with a woman.

270
00:11:21,840 --> 00:11:22,440
You alright, Young Master Gao?

271
00:11:22,559 --> 00:11:23,799
Yudie.

272
00:11:24,559 --> 00:11:25,080
Sanniang.

273
00:11:26,080 --> 00:11:26,799
Spring, Summer, Autumn, Winter.

274
00:11:27,240 --> 00:11:27,639
Alright.

275
00:11:27,799 --> 00:11:28,320
Sanniang.

276
00:11:30,200 --> 00:11:31,440
And Plum, Orchid, Bamboo, Chrysanthemum.

277
00:11:31,879 --> 00:11:32,879
That's eight of them!

278
00:11:34,440 --> 00:11:35,600
Yudie.

279
00:11:44,240 --> 00:11:44,919
Young Master.

280
00:11:45,559 --> 00:11:47,000
This is the finest Apricot Blossom Rain.

281
00:11:47,440 --> 00:11:48,159
Please, have a taste.

282
00:12:02,720 --> 00:12:04,159
I wonder if I might have the honor

283
00:12:05,279 --> 00:12:06,440
of seeing your true face, my lady.

284
00:12:34,279 --> 00:12:36,919
Through ages, no peerless beauty endures,

285
00:12:37,879 --> 00:12:40,480
Yet a fair maiden delights the eye.

286
00:12:41,360 --> 00:12:44,039
A face that topples kingdoms and cities,

287
00:12:45,399 --> 00:12:48,399
Astonishing all under heaven.

288
00:12:50,039 --> 00:12:50,759
Young Master,

289
00:12:51,679 --> 00:12:53,440
do you truly admire me?

290
00:13:11,120 --> 00:13:11,720
Young Master,

291
00:13:13,080 --> 00:13:16,080
this is my very first time.

292
00:13:20,200 --> 00:13:22,759
Just now, my feelings rose unbidden,

293
00:13:23,120 --> 00:13:23,919
and ran ever so deep.

294
00:13:24,399 --> 00:13:25,200
If I have given any offense,

295
00:13:25,840 --> 00:13:27,039
please forgive me, my lady.

296
00:13:28,360 --> 00:13:29,360
Young Master, you misunderstand.

297
00:13:30,080 --> 00:13:32,399
Yudie may hold one of The Twelve Houses,

298
00:13:32,879 --> 00:13:34,360
as long as I remain in the Music Bureau,

299
00:13:34,879 --> 00:13:37,039
my purity will be surrendered eventually.

300
00:13:37,960 --> 00:13:39,399
Young Master, you are so talented,

301
00:13:40,480 --> 00:13:41,200
and Yudie

302
00:13:42,039 --> 00:13:43,840
truly admires you with all her heart.

303
00:13:46,639 --> 00:13:48,840
Allow me to attend to you, Young Master.

304
00:13:57,600 --> 00:13:58,960
I beg you, Young Master,

305
00:14:00,159 --> 00:14:01,200
please be gentle with Yudie.

306
00:14:01,799 --> 00:14:04,960
Flower path was never swept for guests,

307
00:14:06,039 --> 00:14:09,840
today, my humble gate opens for you alone.

